#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:1 maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:33 of
msgid "Purely integer-location based indexing for selection by position."
msgstr "基于纯整数位置的索引，用于按位置选择。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:3 of
msgid ""
"``.iloc[]`` is primarily integer position based (from ``0`` to "
"``length-1`` of the axis), but may also be used with a boolean array."
msgstr ""
"``.iloc[]`` 主要基于整数位置（从轴的 ``0`` 到 ``length-1``），但也可以与"
"布尔数组一起使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:7 of
msgid "Allowed inputs are:"
msgstr "允许的输入包括："

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:9 of
msgid "An integer, e.g. ``5``."
msgstr "一个整数，例如 ``5``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:10 of
msgid "A list or array of integers, e.g. ``[4, 3, 0]``."
msgstr "一个整数列表或数组，例如 ``[4, 3, 0]``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:11 of
msgid "A slice object with ints, e.g. ``1:7``."
msgstr "一个包含整数的切片对象，例如 ``1:7``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:12 of
msgid "A boolean array."
msgstr "一个布尔数组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:13 of
msgid ""
"A ``callable`` function with one argument (the calling Series or "
"DataFrame) and that returns valid output for indexing (one of the above)."
" This is useful in method chains, when you don't have a reference to the "
"calling object, but would like to base your selection on some value."
msgstr ""
"一个带有一个参数（调用的 Series 或 DataFrame）的 ``callable`` 函数，并"
"返回有效的索引输出（上述之一）。这在方法链中很有用，当你没有对调用对象的"
"引用，但希望基于某个值进行选择时。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:18 of
msgid ""
"``.iloc`` will raise ``IndexError`` if a requested indexer is out-of-"
"bounds, except *slice* indexers which allow out-of-bounds indexing (this "
"conforms with python/numpy *slice* semantics)."
msgstr ""
"如果请求的索引器超出范围，``.iloc`` 将引发 ``IndexError``，但 *slice* "
"索引器允许越界索引（这符合 python/numpy *slice* 语义）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:22 of
msgid "See more at :ref:`Selection by Position <indexing.integer>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`按位置选择 <indexing.integer>`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.iat`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:27 of
msgid "Fast integer location scalar accessor."
msgstr "快速整数位置标量访问器。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.loc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:30 of
msgid "Purely label-location based indexer for selection by label."
msgstr "基于纯标签位置的索引器，用于按标签选择。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.iloc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:36 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:48 of
msgid "**Indexing just the rows**"
msgstr "**仅索引行**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:50 of
msgid "With a scalar integer."
msgstr "使用标量整数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:61 of
msgid "With a list of integers."
msgstr "使用整数列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:74 of
msgid "With a `slice` object."
msgstr "使用 `slice` 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:82 of
msgid "With a boolean mask the same length as the index."
msgstr "使用与索引长度相同的布尔掩码。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:89 of
msgid ""
"With a callable, useful in method chains. The `x` passed to the "
"``lambda`` is the DataFrame being sliced. This selects the rows whose "
"index label even."
msgstr ""
"使用 callable，在方法链中很有用。传递给 ``lambda`` 的 `x` 是正在被切片的 "
"DataFrame。这会选择索引标签为偶数的行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:98 of
msgid "**Indexing both axes**"
msgstr "**索引两个轴**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:100 of
msgid ""
"You can mix the indexer types for the index and columns. Use ``:`` to "
"select the entire axis."
msgstr "你可以混合使用索引器类型来索引行和列。使用 ``:`` 来选择整个轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:103 of
msgid "With scalar integers."
msgstr "使用标量整数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:108 of
msgid "With lists of integers."
msgstr "使用整数列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:115 of
msgid "With `slice` objects."
msgstr "使用 `slice` 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:122 of
msgid "With a boolean array whose length matches the columns."
msgstr "使用长度与列匹配的布尔数组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.Series.iloc:130 of
msgid "With a callable function that expects the Series or DataFrame."
msgstr "使用一个可调用函数，该函数需要 Series 或 DataFrame 作为参数。"

